      <h1>About the Project</h1>
      <p><strong>FPNO Navigator</strong> is a Progressive Web App (PWA) prototype built to help new students orient and navigate the Federal Polytechnic Nekede campus. The demo shows a home page, a campus map placeholder, a searchable directory, and this about page.</p>
      <h3>Features (demo)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Installable PWA (manifest + service worker)</li>
        <li>Offline-capable fallback (basic caching)</li>
        <li>Map placeholder (easy upgrade to interactive maps)</li>
        <li>Searchable campus directory</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Your Presenter</h3>
      <p><strong>Mr Godspen</strong> — Events & Spoken Word · Craft — Demo for final-year project defence.</p>

